al Dildar'' || || Bhojpuri ||\n|-\n| 2005 || ''Hum To Ho Gayi Tohar'' || || Bhojpuri ||\n|-\n| 2005 || ''Raja'' || || Bhojpuri ||\n|-\n| 2006 || ''[[Phir Hera Pheri]]'' || Tiwari's sidekick || Hindi || \n|-\n| 2006 || ''Ab Ta Banja Sajanwa Hamaar'' || || Bhojpuri ||\n|-\n| 2006 || ''Banke Bihari M.L.A'' || || Bhojpuri ||\n|-\n| 2006 || ''Ganga'' || || Bhojpuri ||\n|-\n| 2006 || ''Gabbar Singh'' || Govardhan Singh aka Gabbar Singh || Bhojpuri || \n|-\n| 2007 || ''[[Janam Janam Ke Saath]]'' || || Bhojpuri ||\n|-\n| 2007 || ''Deal&nbsp;\u2013 In Crime'' || || Hindi ||\n|-\n| 2007 || ''[[1971 (2007 film)|1971]]'' || Captain Jacob|| Hindi ||\n|-\n| 2008 || ''[[Welcome to Sajjanpur]]'' || Ram Kumar || Hindi ||\n|-\n| 2009 || ''[[Ram Balram (2009 film)|Ram Balram]]'' || || Bhojpuri ||\n|-\n| 2009 || ''[[Luck (2009 film)|Luck]]'' ||Raghav Raghuvaran\n| Hindi ||\n|-\n| 2009 || ''Kanoon Hamra Mutthi Me'' ||  || Bhojpuri ||\n|-\n| 2009 || ''Rangbaaj Daroga'' || || Bhojpuri ||\n|-\n| 2009 || ''Bidai'' || || Bhojpuri ||\n|-\n| 2009 || ''Bhoomiputra'' || || Bhojpuri ||\n|-\n| 2009 || ''Khatailaal Mithai Laal'' || || Bhojpuri ||\n|-\n| 2009 || ''[[Money Hai Toh Honey Hai]]'' || || Hindi ||\n|-\n| 2009 || ''Bihari Mafia'' || || Bhojpuri ||\n|-\n| 2009 || ''Rangbaz Daroga'' || || Bhojpuri ||\n|-\n| 2009 || ''[[Loot (2011 film)|Loot]]'' || || Hindi ||\n|-\n| 2009 || ''Chandu Ki Chameli'' || || Bhojpuri ||\n|-\n| 2009 || ''Dil Diwana Thakur'' || || Bhojpuri ||\n|-\n| 2010 || ''Balidaan'' || || Bhojpuri ||\n|-\n| 2010 || ''Satyamev Jayte'' || || Bhojpuri || \n|-\n| 2010 || ''Mukti'' || || Bhojpuri || \n|-\n| 2010 || ''[[Devra Bada Satawela]]'' || || Bhojpuri || \n|-\n| 2010 || ''Jala Deb Duniya Tohra Pyar Mein'' || || Bhojpuri || \n|-\n| 2010 || ''[[Raavan]]'' || Mangal || Hindi || \n|-\n| 2010 || ''Banaras Ke Babuaa Surat Ke Chhori'' || ||  Bhojpuri || \n|-\n| 2010 ||  ''Ram Pur Ke Lakshman'' || || Bhojpuri || \n|-\n| 2010 || ''Laharia Loota E Rajaji'' || || Bhojpuri || \n|-\n| 2010 |